data.description: Updated main level, private lot/location, and ready to go! Just minutes south of Shakopee, this home sits on a quiet dead-end street, giving the home and lot a quiet and private feel.  Offering three bedrooms on an updated main level, this home is great for families! Be sure to check out the oversized master bedroom with its own private deck overlooking the backyard!   The lower level is unfinished and provides all kinds of options to add immediate equity!  There is an egress window and walls in place--adding a 4th bedroom would just require a little elbow grease.  Only available due to seller relocation! Book your showing today!
